    <item>
      <title>२२</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarva-prastutiH/1/08/22/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarva-prastutiH/1/08/22/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/vishvAsa-prastutiH/1/08/22/01_adhyAtmikAnyogAnanutiShThennyAyasaMhitAnanaishchArikAn.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;01 अध्यात्मिकान्योगान् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अध्यात्मिकान् योगान् अनुतिष्ठेन् न्याय-संहितान् अनैश्चारिकान् १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;सर्वाष् टीकाः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarvASh_TIkAH/1/08/22/01_adhyAtmikAnyogAnanutiShThennyAyasaMhitAnanaishchArikAn.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;सर्वाष् टीकाः ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Bühler&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;He shall employ the means which tend to the acquisition of (the knowledge of) the Ātman, which are attended by the consequent (destruction of the passions, and) which prevent the wandering (of the mind from its object, and fix it on the contemplation of the Ātman). &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;हरदत्त-टीका&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;h5 id=&#34;सतरम&#34;&gt;सूत्रम्&lt;/h5&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अध्यात्मिकान् योगाननुतिष्ठेन्न्यायसंहिताननैश्चारिकान् ॥ १ ॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>२३</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarva-prastutiH/1/08/23/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarva-prastutiH/1/08/23/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;true&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;3&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/vishvAsa-prastutiH/1/08/23/01_Atman_pashyan_sarvabhUtAni.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h3&gt;01 आत्मन् पश्यन् सर्वभूतानि ...{Loading}...&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;आत्मन् पश्यन् सर्वभूतानि न मुह्येच्चिन्तयन्कविः । आत्मानं चैव सर्वत्र यः पश्येत्स वै ब्रह्मा नाकपृष्ठे विराजति १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;सर्वाष् टीकाः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarvASh_TIkAH/1/08/23/01_Atman_pashyan_sarvabhUtAni.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;सर्वाष् टीकाः ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Bühler&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;That Brāhmaṇa, who is wise and recognises all creatures to be in the Ātman, who pondering (thereon) does not become bewildered, and who recognises the Ātman in every (created) thing, shines, indeed, in heaven.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;हरदत्त-टीका&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;h5 id=&#34;सतरम&#34;&gt;सूत्रम्&lt;/h5&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;आत्मन् पश्यन् सर्वभूतानि न मुह्येच्चिन्तयन्कविः।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;आत्मानं चैव सर्वत्र यः पश्यत्स वै ब्रह्मा नाकपृष्ठे विराजति ॥ ९ ॥ १ ॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
